<TITLE>MALCOLM WALLOP -- Heritage </TITLE>

<H3>MALCOLM WALLOP</H3>
<B>DISTINGUISHED FELLOW</B>
<P><IMG SRC="/heritage/staff/pics/wallop.jpe" ALIGN=LEFT HSPACE=10>
<P>
A former three-term United States Senator from Wyoming, Wallop works with Heritage's policy team to develop alternatives to the administration's strategic defense plans. He is a former member of the Senate Armed Services and Select Intelligence Committees, and the Senate Finance, Small Business, and Energy and Natural Resources Committees. He also works with Heritage experts in the areas of property rights and environmental policy.

