<html>

<TITLE>Guest Columnists</title>

<BODY bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/paper2.jpg">



<center>

<a href="/cgi-bin/redir?SpaceID=9&AdID=26&URL=http://www.socialcritic.com"><img src="/ads/socialcritic/animated bias-soc.gif" border=0 width=110 height=120 alt="Tired of Liberal Bias?"></a>

